	"Ą Eudoramail will open your web browser and take you to our Payment & Registration pageĄ You'll be asked to provide your payment and registration information on the web siteĄ We'll then email a Eudoramail registration code back to youĄ The next time you check mail, Eudoramail will automatically recognize this code and display a dialog box inviting you to confirm your registration informationĄ Ta-da!  You'll then become a Paid mode user...  Congratulations!"
